comments: Monk (LAL) makes legal contact with the ball followed by incidental contact with Wiggins' (GSW) right arm after the release of his post shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Westbrook (LAL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Wiggins (GSW) brushes Anthony's (LAL) left arm prior to briefly applying a hand to his back, and marginal contact occurs. This contact is followed by illegal contact made by Anthony.
Anthony (LAL) reaches around Wiggins (GSW) with his off-arm and hooks him.
Anthony (LAL) applies a hand to Curry's (GSW) front during the drive, and marginal contact occurs.
Anthony (LAL) makes incidental contact with Curry's (GSW) right arm after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
James (LAL) splits his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Westbrook (LAL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes into the backcourt.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Kuminga (GSW) briefly grasps James' (LAL) jersey before releasing, and marginal contact occurs.
